<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Google Review AI for <%= industryName %> | ReviewGhost</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Google+Sans:wght@400;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Google Sans', sans-serif; background: #ffffff; color: #3c4043; }
        .hero-section { padding: 100px 0; background: radial-gradient(circle at 10% 90%, #fce8e6 0%, #ffffff 40%); }
        .btn-google { background: #1a73e8; color: white; padding: 12px 30px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 500; border: none; }
        .btn-google:hover { background: #1765cc; color: white; }
        .keyword-highlight { color: #EA4335; background: #fce8e6; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; }
        .trust-badge { background: #f8f9fa; border-radius: 50px; padding: 10px 20px; display: inline-block; font-size: 0.9rem; margin-bottom: 20px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg py-3 sticky-top bg-white border-bottom">
    <div class="container">
        <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold fs-3" href="/">
            <span style="color: #4285F4">R</span><span style="color: #EA4335">e</span><span style="color: #FBBC05">v</span><span style="color: #4285F4">i</span><span style="color: #34A853">e</span><span style="color: #EA4335">w</span>Ghost
        </a>
        <div class="d-flex align-items-center gap-3">
            <a href="/dashboard" class="btn btn-google">Try for <%= industryName %></a>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<section class="hero-section text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="trust-badge text-danger fw-medium">🎯 Purpose-built for <%= industryName %> businesses</div>
        <h1 class="display-3 fw-bold mb-4" style="letter-spacing: -1px;">Rank your <span class="text-primary"><%= industryName %></span> <br>Higher on Google Maps</h1>
        <p class="lead text-secondary mb-5 mx-auto" style="max-width: 700px;">
            Stop copying and pasting generic replies. Our AI detects languages and injects <span class="keyword-highlight">Local SEO keywords</span> specific to <%= industryName.toLowerCase() %> to turn reviews into revenue.
        </p>
        <div class="d-flex justify-content-center gap-3">
            <button class="btn btn-google btn-lg" onclick="location.href='/dashboard'">Start Free Trial</button>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-5 text-start bg-light p-4 rounded-3 border mx-auto" style="max-width: 600px;">
            <p class="small text-uppercase fw-bold text-secondary mb-2">⚡ AI Magic for <%= industryName %></p>
            <p class="mb-0"><strong>Customer:</strong> "The wait time was long but the service was great."</p>
            <hr>
            <p class="mb-0 text-success fw-medium"><strong>ReviewGhost AI:</strong> "Thank you! We're thrilled you enjoyed our service. As a leading <%= industryName.toLowerCase() %> in the area, we are constantly working on reducing wait times. See you next time!"</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

</body>
</html>
